Description automatically generated</svg:desc>
    </draw:frame></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35" loext:marker-style-name="T9"/>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_1" text:outline-level="1"><text:bookmark-start text:name="_Toc228363884"/>Building a Keyboard App for iOS<text:bookmark-end text:name="_Toc228363884"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard" loext:marker-style-name="T19"><text:span text:style-name="T19">The process for building an Android App on a Mac follows the steps laid out in </text:span><text:bookmark-start text:name="OLE_LINK31"/><text:bookmark-start text:name="OLE_LINK30"/><text:span text:style-name="T43">the Keyboard App Builder 02 Building Apps</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span><text:bookmark-end text:name="OLE_LINK31"/><text:bookmark-end text:name="OLE_LINK30"/><text:span text:style-name="T19">document. <text:s/>Building one for iOS has several additional considerations, including getting provisioning profiles for app.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P44" text:outline-level="2" loext:marker-style-name="T9"><text:bookmark-start text:name="_Toc228363885"/><text:bookmark-start text:name="OLE_LINK29"/><text:bookmark-start text:name="OLE_LINK28"/><text:span text:style-name="T9">Apple Development Store Setup</text:span><text:bookmark-end text:name="_Toc228363885"/><text:span text:style-name="T9"/></text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3" loext:marker-style-name="T9"><text:bookmark-end text:name="OLE_LINK28"/><text:bookmark-end text:name="OLE_LINK29"/><text:bookmark-start text:name="OLE_LINK18"/><text:bookmark-start text:name="OLE_LINK17"/><text:bookmark-start text:name="_Toc228363886"/><text:span text:style-name="T9">Enroll in the Apple Developer Program</text:span><text:bookmark-end text:name="OLE_LINK18"/><text:bookmark-end text:name="OLE_LINK17"/><text:bookmark-end text:name="_Toc228363886"/><text:span text:style-name="T9"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard" loext:marker-style-name="T18"><text:span text:style-name="T18">To build iOS apps and distribute them through the Apple App Store, you will need to be enrolled in the Apple Developer Program. You can do this as either (i) an individual, or (ii) an organisation. The cost is USD $99 per year.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P19" loext:marker-style-name="T18"><text:span text:style-name="T18">To enroll:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"/></text:p>
   <text:list text:style-name="WWNum37">
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P62" loext:marker-style-name="T18"><text:span text:style-name="T18">Go to </text:span><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://developer.apple.com/programs/enroll/" text:style-name="ListLabel_20_436" text:visited-style-name="ListLabel_20_436"><text:span text:style-name="T44">https://developer.apple.com/programs/enroll/</text:span></text:a></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P63" loext:marker-style-name="T18"><text:span text:style-name="T18">Press the </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T42">Start Your Enrollment</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"> button to start.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3" loext:marker-style-name="T9"><text:bookmark-start text:name="_Toc228363887"/><text:span text:style-name="T9">Create Signing Certificate</text:span><text:bookmark-end text:name="_Toc228363887"/><text:span text:style-name="T9"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P64" loext:marker-style-name="T18"><text:span text:style-name="T18">When you create an iOS app, it needs to be signed with a certificate.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P65" loext:marker-style-name="T18"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard" loext:marker-style-name="T18"><text:span text:style-name="T18">To create a certificate:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"/></text:p>
   <text:list text:style-name="WWNum13">
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P66" loext:marker-style-name="T18"><text:span text:style-name="T18">Go to the </text:span><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://developer.apple.com/" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Internet_20_link"><text:span text:style-name="T18">Apple Developer</text:span></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T18"> website and log in to your account if you are not already.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P66" loext:marker-style-name="T18"><text:span text:style-name="T18">Select </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T42">Certificates, Identifiers &amp; Profiles</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P66" loext:marker-style-name="T33"><text:span text:style-name="T33">Click the</text:span><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr2" draw:name="Picture 1127969481" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.1945in" svg:height="0.2362in"><draw:image draw:mime-type="image/png">
